### Create a Seller
POST http://localhost:3000/query/sellers
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Madeline Torres",
    "email": "madeline@example.com",
    "shop_name": "Madeline Handmade Gifts Shop"
}

### Create a Product (Replace `seller_id` with actual ID)
POST http://localhost:3000/query/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "seller_id": "4b390fe3-29b3-42fe-82c9-f7456d359a03",
    "name": "Handmade Ceramic Mug",
    "description": "A beautifully designed ceramic mug",
    "price": 15.99,
    "stock": 20,
    "image_url": "/images/mug.jpg"
}

### Get All Sellers
GET http://localhost:3000/query/sellers

### Get All Products
GET http://localhost:3000/query/products
